<h3 id="html">HTML</h3>
<p>HTML (HyperText Markup Language) is the most basic building block of the Web. 
It describes and defines the content of a webpage. HTML elements are represented by tags.</p>

<p>Written using tags enclosed in angle brackets</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;html&gt;</span></code> called opening tag</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;/html&gt;</code> called closing tag</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;!-- comment --&gt;</code></p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
