</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="cp">&lt;!doctype html&gt;</span> <span class="c">&lt;!-- instruction to the browser about what version of HTML the page is written in.--&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;html&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;head&gt;</span> <span class="c">&lt;!-- title,scripts, styles, meta information, and more. --&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;meta</span> <span class="na">charset=</span><span class="s">"UTF-8"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;title&gt;</span>Sample<span class="nt">&lt;/title&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;/head&gt;</span>

  <span class="nt">&lt;body&gt;</span>
